flowchart TD
    A[User opens /pseudo] --> B{Project selected?}
    B -- No --> C[Show project dropdown\nno file tree visible]
    C --> D[User selects project]
    D --> E[Load file list\nGET /api/pseudo/files]
    B -- Yes --> E
    E --> F{Files found?}
    F -- No --> G[Empty state:\nRun /pseudocode all]
    F -- Yes --> H[Render file tree\n239 files]

    H --> I{URL has path?}
    I -- No --> J[Tree visible\nno file selected]
    I -- Yes --> K[Load file\nGET /api/pseudo/file]
    K --> L[Parse .pseudo text\ninto blocks]
    L --> M[Render viewer\n+ function jump panel]

    J --> N[User clicks file in tree]
    N --> O[Push to browser history\nURL: /pseudo/src/mcp/setup]
    O --> K

    M --> P{User action}
    P -- Click CALLS link --> Q[Push to history\nLoad target file]
    Q --> K
    P -- Hover CALLS link 400ms --> R[Fetch target file\nif not cached]
    R --> S[Show popover:\ntitle + exports]
    S --> T{User clicks popover?}
    T -- Yes --> Q
    T -- No --> U[Dismiss on mouse leave]
    P -- Browser back/fwd --> V[URL changes\nReact Router re-renders]
    V --> K
    P -- Search Cmd+K --> W[Open search dropdown]
    W --> X[User types query\nGET /api/pseudo/search]
    X --> Y[Show grouped results]
    Y --> Z[User selects result]
    Z --> Q
    P -- Click function in jump panel --> AA[Smooth scroll\nto function block]
    P -- Change project --> AB[New project selected\nURL resets to /pseudo]
    AB --> E
